35:55.254 --> 35:58.490
...could you please start
making the drops again?

35:58.524 --> 36:03.795
No club, no cocaine, hermano.

36:03.829 --> 36:06.565
*

36:27.986 --> 36:30.522
*

36:45.904 --> 36:46.972
Wait!

36:50.742 --> 36:52.177
You okay?

36:56.682 --> 36:58.317
(grunts)

36:58.350 --> 37:01.219
Yeah.

37:01.253 --> 37:03.221
You were talking in your sleep.

37:06.258 --> 37:07.893
Oh, yeah?

37:07.926 --> 37:09.328
(clears throat)

37:09.361 --> 37:10.962
What'd I say?

37:10.996 --> 37:13.532
You said "Wait."

37:24.376 --> 37:27.379
Tulfowitz pulled out.

37:28.414 --> 37:30.081
Got the call today.

37:30.115 --> 37:31.750
The building's ours.

37:31.783 --> 37:34.920
(laughs softly)

37:34.953 --> 37:36.955
That's great.

37:38.223 --> 37:40.426
Right?

37:40.459 --> 37:42.694
Mm-hmm.

37:45.130 --> 37:47.132
Come on, Mama.

37:51.403 --> 37:55.541
That man treated you
like a slave for 15 years.

37:55.574 --> 37:58.109
Took advantage of good,
honest people.

37:58.143 --> 38:00.111
Shit, he sent men over here
to mess us up,

38:00.145 --> 38:01.613
and we took care of them.

38:01.647 --> 38:03.682
You mean to tell me
it don't feel great

38:03.715 --> 38:05.283
to put that asshole
in his place?

38:05.317 --> 38:07.953
-Franklin...
-Come on.

38:07.986 --> 38:10.456
I mean, even just a little bit.

38:10.489 --> 38:12.290
Just the tiniest bit great, huh?

38:12.324 --> 38:14.292
-(laughs)
-Boy, get out my face.

38:14.326 --> 38:16.328
Mwah.

38:19.498 --> 38:21.833
We did it.

38:25.471 --> 38:27.639
You did it.

38:27.673 --> 38:29.675
Later, Mama.

38:31.977 --> 38:34.346
(door opens)

38:36.382 --> 38:39.385
-How'd it go?
-Not great. Not great.

38:39.418 --> 38:41.252
Could've been, you know,
could've been better, but

38:41.286 --> 38:43.288
it's like...
Here's the thing I realized.

38:43.321 --> 38:45.323
These people, they don't want
to listen to reason,

38:45.357 --> 38:46.692
so you can't reason with them.

38:46.725 --> 38:47.993
Like, I don't even know
why I'm surprised.

38:48.026 --> 38:49.995
What am I surprised about, even?

38:50.028 --> 38:51.663
I should just be relieved
that he didn't try

38:51.697 --> 38:53.699
-to force me to do more cocaine.
-You did cocaine?

38:53.732 --> 38:55.967
Mm. I did cocaine.

38:56.001 --> 38:57.503
I did cocaine.

38:57.536 --> 38:59.337
I mean, I didn't want to, but
he insisted, and I'm... like,

38:59.371 --> 39:00.506
I'm sitting there,
and I'm thinking, you know,

39:00.539 --> 39:01.940
if-if that's
what it's gonna take to get

39:01.973 --> 39:03.308
the drops back on, then, yeah,
I'll do the fucking cocaine.

39:03.341 --> 39:05.911
-So the drops are back on?
-No!

39:05.944 --> 39:08.246
The-the drops are not back on,
Julia, that's what I'm saying.

39:08.279 --> 39:10.281
-Are you listening to me?
-I'm listening to you.

39:10.315 --> 39:12.651
Calm down. Jesus, take a breath.

39:12.684 --> 39:16.655
(exhaling)

39:16.688 --> 39:18.457
Sorry.

39:18.490 --> 39:19.858
Okay.

39:19.891 --> 39:22.360
I know that I said
that I didn't want you

39:22.394 --> 39:24.530
to meet with the Colombians,
but I do think

39:24.563 --> 39:26.965
-that I'm gonna need
your help on this.
-Sure.

39:26.998 --> 39:30.168
I... That's what I'm here for.

39:30.201 --> 39:32.203
What do you need?

39:32.237 --> 39:35.206
(sunglasses clatter)

39:35.240 --> 39:37.576
What do you know
about nightclubs?

39:37.609 --> 39:39.611
(siren wailing in distance)

39:52.424 --> 39:54.392
-What's wrong?
-My daddy acting crazy.

39:54.426 --> 39:56.394
He's sending me to Spelman
this weekend.

39:56.428 --> 39:58.396
-How come?
-I don't know.

39:58.430 --> 40:00.398
-Well, ask him.
-SHON-SHON: Hey, One Time!

40:00.432 --> 40:02.167
The fuck you doing here, bitch?

40:02.200 --> 40:04.069
-"Bitch"?
-You know your daddy
and the rest

40:04.102 --> 40:07.172
of them pigs snatched up
my cousin, fucked up his house.

40:07.205 --> 40:08.740
-What you got to say about that?
-EVA: Stop tripping,

40:08.774 --> 40:10.375
Shon-Shon.
You know she ain't got nothing

40:10.408 --> 40:12.010
-to do with that.
-The fuck she don't.

40:12.043 --> 40:13.645
I'm gonna go.

40:13.679 --> 40:15.814
-Hey, I'm talking to you!
-Shon-Shon...

40:15.847 --> 40:18.684
Don't walk away from me.

40:18.717 --> 40:21.186
I ain't doing this with you,
Shon-Shon.

40:21.219 --> 40:22.721
-Yes, you is.
-What?

40:22.754 --> 40:24.556
-What the fuck?
-Bitch!

40:24.590 --> 40:25.691
(grunting, thuds)

40:30.762 --> 40:32.931
You want one?

40:32.964 --> 40:34.966
Nah, I'm good.

40:41.106 --> 40:43.108
-Look...
-Before you say anything,

40:43.141 --> 40:47.112
I just want to say
I appreciate you.

40:47.145 --> 40:50.048
I know, a lot of people
take a beating like that,

40:50.081 --> 40:52.083
they want out the game.

40:58.590 --> 41:01.392
I'm concerned
about my shop, nephew.

41:03.294 --> 41:06.031
I put a lot of money in that
thing. I need it to work out.

41:07.165 --> 41:10.769
You and Cissy,
you got the real estate thing.

41:10.802 --> 41:12.237
Louie got the club.

41:12.270 --> 41:14.973
Jammin' Jeromes?

41:15.006 --> 41:17.408
That's my shit.

41:19.310 --> 41:21.279
Need to give it
my full attention.

41:22.313 --> 41:23.749
Can't be no old nigga

41:23.782 --> 41:25.751
out here slinging rocks
on the block, man.

41:25.784 --> 41:29.154
Man, that's why I'm trying to
get this wholesale thing going.

41:29.187 --> 41:33.592
So we can make that money and
never have to be on the street.

41:33.625 --> 41:36.127
L.A. first, then we'll expand.

41:36.161 --> 41:40.198
Detroit, New York, Chicago.

41:40.231 --> 41:43.434
Making money
and staying in the house.

41:43.468 --> 41:45.436
Like them
white motherfuckers do. Huh?

41:45.470 --> 41:48.473
-We ain't no goddamn
white motherfuckers.
-Listen, Unc.

41:50.508 --> 41:55.113
We close, so close,
but we're not there yet.

41:55.146 --> 41:58.483
And I need you in this with me.

41:59.484 --> 42:02.053
All right?

42:03.789 --> 42:07.158
I remember when you were
selling dime bags of shake.

42:07.192 --> 42:08.860
(laughs)

42:08.894 --> 42:10.962
Yeah, that I got from you.

42:13.098 --> 42:15.533
We gonna be all right.

42:16.568 --> 42:19.170
I got you.

42:19.204 --> 42:21.539
(train whistle blowing
in distance)

42:45.597 --> 42:47.699
(sighs)
What's up, Sarge?

42:47.733 --> 42:52.303
What are you doing out here?

42:52.337 --> 42:54.305
Rat Squad go hard on you
or what?

42:56.374 --> 42:58.509
I'm suspended.

43:00.545 --> 43:04.916
(exhales) Fucking Todd,
that piece of shit.

43:04.950 --> 43:07.919
I need you to do something
for me, Nix.

43:07.953 --> 43:10.021
Name it.

43:11.256 --> 43:14.025
I'm gonna bury Franklin Saint.

43:16.227 --> 43:18.396
About fucking time.

43:18.429 --> 43:20.065
What are you thinking?

43:20.098 --> 43:22.500
Can't plant evidence on him.

43:22.533 --> 43:25.103
Kid's got somebody up high
protecting him.

43:25.136 --> 43:26.772
And everybody knows
I'm gunning for him,

43:26.805 --> 43:30.008
so we got to tread lightly.

43:30.041 --> 43:33.611
I'm-a need you to find out
where he lays his head.

43:33.645 --> 43:37.615
He's not staying with his uncle
or his mama anymore.

43:37.649 --> 43:40.385
I can do that. Then what?

43:43.922 --> 43:46.091
Then get your wife and kids
out of town

43:46.124 --> 43:51.362
for a couple of days,
and we go to work.

43:51.396 --> 43:53.932
*

45:28.226 --> 45:30.195
Captioned by
Media Access Group at WGBH

45:33.999 --> 45:35.733
This is business.
Let's make some money.

45:37.268 --> 45:41.672
I will bring you all down,
one... by... one.

45:41.706 --> 45:43.441
FRANKLIN: Playin'
a different game now.
